latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Summer Skin Care Routine.
It's time to purify your skin YOURSELF!
.
.
If you are fed up of acne problems and skin irritations then it surely needs help !
And NEEM is your savoir !
.
.
Take 2 tbspn of neem powder , mix it with 2 tbspn of water ( You can use rose water or cucumber water instead) and apply it all over your face ! 
Let it dry for 10 to 15 mins then wash off !
( If you have dry skin , replace rose water with turmeric powder )
After you wash your face ,
Apply Moisturizer and massage your face and lastly spray rose water on your face ! .
Your skin is now miles away from bacteria , is clam and free from acne !
.
Your skin glows differently too ! .
Products used :-
@neutrogena Face Wash
@khadinatural NeemFace Pack
@neutrogena  Hydro Boost Gel
.
